# profileName

**Instance Property**

The name assigned to the profile.

## Declaration

```swift
var profileName: String? { get }
```

## Discussion

Use this property to retrieve the settings if your vehicle supports saving named profiles.

## Getting the Profile Information

- **isDefaultProfile**: A Boolean value indicating whether to make the profile the default profile.
- **profileNumber**: The profile index from which to restore the settings.
- **profileLabel**: The name assigned to the profile.
